     match (or significant overlap in the case of single exon transcripts)\n\
+ --terminal-delta <d> : like --strict-match but uses <d> as the terminal-end\n\
+    tolerance for the transcript-level '=' code, INDEPENDENTLY of -e (which\n\
+    stays tied to exon-level accuracy); makes Transcript-level Sn/Sp\n\
